text:
I've visited the Great Dane dozens of times. I've never had a bad experience. 
The restaurant is an inviting, clean environment; 
the staff are patient and efficient; 
the food is made with good quality ingredients; 
the menu offers a wide variety of choices; 
prices are reasonable. 
Once, When a dish came out of the kitchen not-quite as expected, the staff brought out a new plate and adjusted the bill.
The Sunday brunch is fantastic!
